summary: An Ordinance approving and confirming the plat of Fauntelroy Scenic Addition, to The City of Seattle, executed on the 26th day of April, 1909, by C. B. Klaus and Floy E. Klaus, his wife, and J. W. Cline, and Jennie Cline, his wife, the Century Realty Company; W. W. Watters, President and C. R. Keck, Secretary and Irving T. Alvord, Mortgagee and Peter Brown, a bachelor.
